benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/bundles/{bundleId}/renameKey - Update a bundle externalKey

covered: Valid Request: TC01 demonstrates successful update of a bundle externalKey with a 204 response and updated value.
Non-Existing Resource: TC04 and TC15 verify 404 when the bundle does not exist or there are no bundles in the system.
Authorization: TC12 ensures proper unauthorized handling (401/403) and TC02 covers missing required header (400).
Error Handling and Validation: TC03 (invalid bundleId format), TC06 (missing body), TC07 (malformed JSON), TC08 (missing externalKey), TC11 (empty externalKey).
Conflict and Validation: TC05 demonstrates externalKey conflict (400).

Edge Cases: TC09 (extra fields), TC10 (extKey length handling), TC19 (special characters), TC20 (leading/trailing spaces), TC21 (additional unexpected header) demonstrate flexibility and validation edge cases.
Large Payload and Performance: TC16 tests large payload handling and TC23 validates response time under load.
Concurrency: TC17 tests concurrent updates to the same bundle.
Integration/Resilience: TC13 covers 503 service unavailable when dependencies fail.
Header Details: TC14 validates handling of X-Killbill-Reason and X-Killbill-Comment headers.
Regression/Backward Compatibility: TC18 and TC22 address handling of problematic keys and legacy clients.
Documentation: TC24 ensures API documentation is accessible.
gaps: Rate limiting / throttling scenarios are not covered.
Caching behavior (ETag/Cache-Control) testing is not covered.
Partial update semantics beyond updating externalKey (unknown fields handling under strict mode) is not clearly tested beyond TC09.
Internal server error (500) testing is not present (only 503 is covered).
Soft deletes or data retention semantics not addressed.
Explicit access token expiry/invalid tokens beyond missing header coverage.
recommendations: Add rate-limiting and throttling tests to verify behavior under bursts.
Add caching validation tests (ETag/If-None-Match with 304) to exercise caching behavior.
Introduce tests for 500 Internal Server Error scenarios to complement 503.
Clarify and test partial update semantics and behavior with extra/unknown fields (strict vs lenient).
Add explicit concurrency error tests (409) for conflicting renames.
Extend authorization coverage to include invalid/expired tokens and token refresh flows.
